title: Bot Duo LF Top/Mid/Jg for OOL Team.
body:
EDIT: Roster has been filled. Still looking for highish ranked substitute players.

Looking for players to play in the Oceanic Open Ladder. 
No ranked requirements. We are currently Silver 3 & Silver 5, so we'll just be playing for the experience and to have fun. 

Only thing necessary is that you are dedicated and available to play on each of the tournament dates.
Round 1	June 11th/12th
Round 2	June 25th/26th
Round 3	July 9th/10th
Round 4	July 23rd/24th

Roles that need to be filled.
Top
Jungle
Mid

We are also able to have 3 Substitute players.

Add me in game (Alfie) or leave an application below :)
